{"tid":2231204,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"12港人送中︱黃店自發製作#save12hkyouth鎖匙扣 民主派區議員派街坊冀持續關注","createTime":"2020-10-05T13:14:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T16:31:26.000Z","uid":240362,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"eeb80f752686b2cec9e012b60509d01ee93c4822","tid":2231204,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T13:14:43.000Z","msg":"12名港人涉潛逃被扣深圳已44天，有黃店自發製作「#save12hkyouth」鎖匙扣，獲民主派區議員響應派發，希望港人持續關注事件。<br />\n<br />\n有份派發鎖匙扣的沙田區議員陳兆陽表示，涉事港人家屬委託律師，一直要求與當事人會面但不果，而在中國司法制度下，香港民間「都做唔到乜嘢」，惟他盼港人不忘關注，「如果唔係就會有第13個、14個、15個」。<br />\n<br />\n部份民主派人士早前發起中秋「一人一明信片」行動，去信聲援12名被拘內地的港人，沙田區議員陳兆陽今日（5日）在社交網站發文，稱免費派發印有「#save12hkyouth」的鎖匙扣，希望市民務必帶在身上、掛在背包，以喚起身邊人共同關注事件。<br />\n<br />\n陳兆陽接受《蘋果》查詢時表示，有本地衣物印刷黃店自發製作鎖匙扣，並聯絡區議員代為派發，目前有數名沙田區議員協助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201005/6GK34CAT4JD3NDTK6WSYKQC2WQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201005%2F6GK34CAT4JD3NDTK6WSYKQC2WQ%2F&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZL3Kg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=51db051a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201005%2F6GK34CAT4JD3NDTK6WSYKQC2WQ%2F&h=f91c48e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201005/6GK34CAT4JD3NDTK6WSYKQC2WQ/</a>"},{"pid":"0b8d5e3d6b5a034eedb13990ed3dfa9ad7d324d1","tid":2231204,"uid":219969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T13:14:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"023023437a6d0f356c87a09f3950f9fde283ee98","tid":2231204,"uid":271497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T13:15:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5992b7097042b98b7d77cb7bf68f761742f27b99","tid":2231204,"uid":271497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b8d5e3d6b5a034eedb13990ed3